title: Bindi Irwin Honors Late Dad Steve Irwin on His 55th Birthday (PHOTOS)
text:
NEXT Advertisement 
Bindi Irwin posted a sweet tribute to her late father, Steve Irwin, on what would’ve been his 55th birthday. 
The Crocodile Hunter passed away in September 2006 after a stingray’s barb pierced him in the chest. 
Flip through the gallery above to see the Dancing With the Stars champ’s post and 21 other times she honored her dad on Instagram.
